      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Improve doctor runtime and schema drift diagnostics",
        "body": "Closes #85.\n\nAdds read-only doctor JSON diagnostics for the active executable/runtime identity and local DB schema state, including supported/current versions, pending/newer migration flags, PR-detail storage support, and concise drift next steps.\n\nKeeps schema inspection diagnostic-only so `doctor --json` can report missing, newer, or legacy stores without applying migrations.\n\nDoctor JSON contract: scripts should inspect `db_schema.state` and `source_db_schema.state` for schema health. When `runtime_open_error` is present, `doctor --json` still emits the runtime identity plus read-only schema diagnostics so automation can report drift instead of losing the diagnostic payload.\n\nBehavior proof from a branch-built macOS arm64 binary at `0a02a2ae636e`:\n\nCurrent database excerpt:\n```json\n{\n  \"runtime\": {\n    \"build_revision\": \"0a02a2ae636e7f7da4b491acb2f53cc109e9bc77\",\n    \"module_path\": \"github.com/openclaw/gitcrawl\",\n    \"version\": \"dev\"\n  },\n  \"db_schema\": {\n    \"current_version\": 4,\n    \"supported_version\": 4,\n    \"state\": \"current\",\n    \"current\": true,\n    \"pending_migration\": false,\n    \"newer\": false,\n    \"pr_details\": {\n      \"files_position_key\": true,\n      \"duplicate_path_files_supported\": true,\n      \"state\": \"supported\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nLegacy drift excerpt:\n```json\n{\n  \"db_schema\": {\n    \"current_version\": 3,\n    \"supported_version\": 4,\n    \"state\": \"pending_migration\",\n    \"pending_migration\": true,\n    \"legacy\": true,\n    \"pending_migrations\": [\"schema_version_3_to_4\"],\n    \"next_steps\": [\"Run a write-path command with the intended rebuilt gitcrawl executable to apply pending migrations.\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\nNewer drift excerpt:\n```json\n{\n  \"db_schema\": {\n    \"current_version\": 99,\n    \"supported_version\": 4,\n    \"state\": \"newer\",\n    \"newer\": true,\n    \"next_steps\": [\"Upgrade the active gitcrawl executable to a build that supports this database schema.\"]\n  },\n  \"runtime_open_error\": \"database schema version 99 is newer than supported version 4\"\n}\n```\n",
        "branch": "gitcrawl-doctor-runtime-schema-85",
